
---

# 🛑 .gitignore (Use for BOTH Projects)

Create `.gitignore` file in each project root:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.so

# Virtual Environment
venv/
.env/
.envrc/

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# PyTorch Models
*.pth
*.pt

# Logs
*.log

# OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Large Dataset Folders
data/
datasets/
archive/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# PyCharm
.idea/